*Sistem* je kompleksan i skup instrumenta, regulacija i procedura. (The system is complex and expensive instrument, regulations and procedures.)

Ovaj *sistem* je odgovoran za bezbednost i integritet podataka. (This system is responsible for the security and integrity of the data.)

Kompanija je implementirala novi *sistem* za rad sa klijentima. (The company implemented a new system for working with customers.)

Ovaj *sistem* je jedinstven u svojoj vrsti. (This system is unique in its kind.)

Kompanija je unapredila svoj *sistem* za obradu podataka. (The company has improved its system for data processing.)